com.ibm.disni.rdma.verbs

类 IbvWC

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibm.disni.rdma.verbs.IbvWC

  • public class IbvWC
extends Object
    Represents a work completion event. Application will use the pollCQ verbs call to query for completion events.
